SKILL.md를 확인했습니다. 이제 Maum 앱의 전체 데이터 모델 설계를 진행합니다.

---

# Maum 앱 전체 데이터 모델 설계

## 1. 사용자/프로필 도메인

### MySQL 스키마 (JPA Entity 관점)

**users 테이블**
```sql
CREATE TABLE users (
    id            BIGINT       NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    uid           VARCHAR(36)  NOT NULL UNIQUE COMMENT '외부 노출용 UUID',
    phone_number  VARCHAR(20)  NOT NULL UNIQUE,
    email         VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE,
    password_hash VARCHAR(255),
    status        ENUM('ACTIVE','SUSPENDED','DELETED') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'ACTIVE',
    role          ENUM('USER','ADMIN') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'USER',
    last_login_at DATETIME,
    created_at    DATETIME     NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    updated_at    DATETIME     NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    deleted_at    DATETIME,
    INDEX idx_uid (uid),
    INDEX idx_phone_number (phone_number),
    INDEX idx_status (status),
    INDEX idx_created_at (created_at)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
```

**profiles 테이블**
```sql
CREATE TABLE profiles (
    id             BIGINT       NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id        BIGINT       NOT NULL UNIQUE,
    nickname       VARCHAR(30)  NOT NULL,
    bio            TEXT,
    birth_date     DATE         NOT NULL,
    gender         ENUM('MALE','FEMALE','OTHER') NOT NULL,
    profile_image  VARCHAR(500),
    voice_intro    VARCHAR(500) COMMENT '음성 자기소개 S3 URL',
    region_code    VARCHAR(10)  COMMENT '지역 코드 (KR-11: 서울 등)',
    latitude       DECIMAL(10,7),
    longitude      DECIMAL(10,7),
    is_location_public BOOLEAN  NOT NULL DEFAULT FALSE,
    call_count     INT          NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
    follower_count INT          NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
    following_count INT         NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
    like_count     INT          NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
    created_at     DATETIME     NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    updated_at     DATETIME     NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    CONSTRAINT fk_profiles_user FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(id),
    INDEX idx_user_id (user_id),
    INDEX idx_nickname (nickname),
    INDEX idx_gender (gender),
    INDEX idx_region_code (region_code),
    INDEX idx_location (latitude, longitude)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
```

**match_preferences 테이블**
```sql
CREATE TABLE match_preferences (
    id                BIGINT  NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id           BIGINT  NOT NULL UNIQUE,
    preferred_gender  ENUM('MALE','FEMALE','ANY') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'ANY',
    min_age           TINYINT NOT NULL DEFAULT 18,
    max_age           TINYINT NOT NULL DEFAULT 99,
    preferred_region  VARCHAR(10),
    max_distance_km   INT     NOT NULL DEFAULT 50,
    call_purpose      ENUM('FRIEND','DATING','ANY') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'ANY',
    is_active         BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT TRUE,
    created_at        DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    updated_at        DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    CONSTRAINT fk_match_prefs_user FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(id),
    INDEX idx_user_id (user_id),
    INDEX idx_preferred_gender (preferred_gender),
    INDEX idx_call_purpose (call_purpose)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
```

**Kotlin JPA Entity**
```kotlin
@Entity
@Table(name = "users")
class User(
    @Id @GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)
    val id: Long = 0,

    @Column(nullable = false, unique = true, length = 36)
    val uid: String = UUID.randomUUID().toString(),

    @Column(name = "phone_number", nullable = false, unique = true, length = 20)
    val phoneNumber: String,

    @Column(unique = true)
    var email: String? = null,

    @Enumerated(EnumType.STRING)
    @Column(nullable = false, length = 20)
    var status: UserStatus = UserStatus.ACTIVE,

    @Enumerated(EnumType.STRING)
    @Column(nullable = false, length = 10)
    val role: UserRole = UserRole.USER,

    @Column(name = "last_login_at")
    var lastLoginAt: LocalDateTime? = null,

    @Column(name = "deleted_at")
    var deletedAt: LocalDateTime? = null,

    @CreationTimestamp
    @Column(name = "created_at", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    val createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @UpdateTimestamp
    @Column(name = "updated_at", nullable = false)
    var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now()
) {
    @OneToOne(mappedBy = "user", cascade = [CascadeType.ALL], fetch = FetchType.LAZY)
    var profile: Profile? = null

    @OneToOne(mappedBy = "user", cascade = [CascadeType.ALL], fetch = FetchType.LAZY)
    var matchPreference: MatchPreference? = null
}

enum class UserStatus { ACTIVE, SUSPENDED, DELETED }
enum class UserRole { USER, ADMIN }

@Entity
@Table(name = "profiles")
class Profile(
    @Id @GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)
    val id: Long = 0,

    @OneToOne(fetch = FetchType.LAZY)
    @JoinColumn(name = "user_id", nullable = false, unique = true)
    val user: User,

    @Column(nullable = false, length = 30)
    var nickname: String,

    @Column(columnDefinition = "TEXT")
    var bio: String? = null,

    @Column(name = "birth_date", nullable = false)
    val birthDate: LocalDate,

    @Enumerated(EnumType.STRING)
    @Column(nullable = false, length = 10)
    val gender: Gender,

    @Column(name = "profile_image", length = 500)
    var profileImage: String? = null,

    @Column(name = "voice_intro", length = 500)
    var voiceIntro: String? = null,

    @Column(name = "region_code", length = 10)
    var regionCode: String? = null,

    @Column(precision = 10, scale = 7)
    var latitude: BigDecimal? = null,

    @Column(precision = 10, scale = 7)
    var longitude: BigDecimal? = null,

    @Column(name = "is_location_public", nullable = false)
    var isLocationPublic: Boolean = false,

    @Column(name = "call_count", nullable = false)
    var callCount: Int = 0,

    @Column(name = "follower_count", nullable = false)
    var followerCount: Int = 0,

    @Column(name = "following_count", nullable = false)
    var followingCount: Int = 0,

    @Column(name = "like_count", nullable = false)
    var likeCount: Int = 0
)

enum class Gender { MALE, FEMALE, OTHER }
```

### Redis 캐시 키 설계 - 사용자/프로필

```
# 사용자 기본 정보 캐시 (TTL: 30분)
user:{userId}                          → User JSON
user:uid:{uid}                         → userId (Long)
user:phone:{phoneNumber}               → userId (Long)

# 프로필 캐시 (TTL: 10분)
profile:{userId}                       → Profile JSON
profile:nickname:{nickname}            → userId (Long)

# 매칭 선호도 캐시 (TTL: 30분)
match_preference:{userId}              → MatchPreference JSON

# 접속 상태 (TTL: 5분, Heartbeat로 갱신)
user:online:{userId}                   → "1" (온라인 여부)
user:online:set                        → ZSET (score: timestamp, member: userId) [활성 사용자 목록]

# 프로필 조회수 (TTL: 24시간)
profile:views:{userId}:{date}         → Integer (조회수)
```

---

## 2. 음성 통화 도메인

### MySQL 스키마

**call_rooms 테이블**
```sql
CREATE TABLE call_rooms (
    id           BIGINT       NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    room_uid     VARCHAR(36)  NOT NULL UNIQUE COMMENT '외부용 Room ID',
    room_type    ENUM('ONE_ON_ONE','GROUP') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'ONE_ON_ONE',
    status       ENUM('WAITING','ACTIVE','ENDED') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'WAITING',
    max_capacity TINYINT      NOT NULL DEFAULT 2,
    created_by   BIGINT       NOT NULL COMMENT 'user_id (방 생성자)',
    started_at   DATETIME,
    ended_at     DATETIME,
    duration_sec INT          COMMENT '실제 통화 시간(초)',
    end_reason   ENUM('NORMAL','TIMEOUT','ERROR','REPORTED') DEFAULT 'NORMAL',
    created_at   DATETIME     NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    updated_at   DATETIME     NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    CONSTRAINT fk_rooms_creator FOREIGN KEY (created_by) REFERENCES users(id),
    INDEX idx_room_uid (room_uid),
    INDEX idx_status (status),
    INDEX idx_created_by (created_by),
    INDEX idx_created_at (created_at)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
```

**call_participants 테이블**
```sql
CREATE TABLE call_participants (
    id            BIGINT  NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    room_id       BIGINT  NOT NULL,
    user_id       BIGINT  NOT NULL,
    role          ENUM('HOST','GUEST') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'GUEST',
    joined_at     DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    left_at       DATETIME,
    duration_sec  INT,
    is_muted      BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT FALSE,
    CONSTRAINT fk_participants_room FOREIGN KEY (room_id) REFERENCES call_rooms(id),
    CONSTRAINT fk_participants_user FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(id),
    UNIQUE KEY uq_room_user (room_id, user_id),
    INDEX idx_room_id (room_id),
    INDEX idx_user_id (user_id),
    INDEX idx_joined_at (joined_at)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
```

**calls 테이블** (개별 통화 이력 - 1:1 기록용)
```sql
CREATE TABLE calls (
    id             BIGINT  NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    room_id        BIGINT  NOT NULL UNIQUE,
    caller_id      BIGINT  NOT NULL COMMENT '발신자 user_id',
    callee_id      BIGINT  NOT NULL COMMENT '수신자 user_id',
    status         ENUM('RINGING','ACCEPTED','REJECTED','MISSED','ENDED') NOT NULL,
    started_at     DATETIME,
    ended_at       DATETIME,
    duration_sec   INT,
    call_quality   TINYINT COMMENT '통화 품질 점수 1~5',
    created_at     DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    CONSTRAINT fk_calls_room   FOREIGN KEY (room_id)   REFERENCES call_rooms(id),
    CONSTRAINT fk_calls_caller FOREIGN KEY (caller_id) REFERENCES users(id),
    CONSTRAINT fk_calls_callee FOREIGN KEY (callee_id) REFERENCES users(id),
    INDEX idx_caller_id (caller_id),
    INDEX idx_callee_id (callee_id),
    INDEX idx_status (status),
    INDEX idx_created_at (created_at)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
```

**Kotlin JPA Entity**
```kotlin
@Entity
@Table(name = "call_rooms")
class CallRoom(
    @Id @GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)
    val id: Long = 0,

    @Column(name = "room_uid", nullable = false, unique = true, length = 36)
    val roomUid: String = UUID.randomUUID().toString(),

    @Enumerated(EnumType.STRING)
    @Column(name = "room_type", nullable = false, length = 15)
    val roomType: RoomType = RoomType.ONE_ON_ONE,

    @Enumerated(EnumType.STRING)
    @Column(nullable = false, length = 10)
    var status: RoomStatus = RoomStatus.WAITING,

    @Column(name = "max_capacity", nullable = false)
    val maxCapacity: Byte = 2,

    @Column(name = "created_by", nullable = false)
    val createdBy: Long,

    @Column(name = "started_at")
    var startedAt: LocalDateTime? = null,

    @Column(name = "ended_at")
    var endedAt: LocalDateTime? = null,

    @Column(name = "duration_sec")
    var durationSec: Int? = null,

    @Enumerated(EnumType.STRING)
    @Column(name = "end_reason", length = 15)
    var endReason: EndReason? = null
) {
    @OneToMany(mappedBy = "room", fetch = FetchType.LAZY)
    val participants: MutableList<CallParticipant> = mutableListOf()
}

enum class RoomType  { ONE_ON_ONE, GROUP }
enum class RoomStatus { WAITING, ACTIVE, ENDED }
enum class EndReason  { NORMAL, TIMEOUT, ERROR, REPORTED }

@Entity
@Table(
    name = "call_participants",
    uniqueConstraints = [UniqueConstraint(columnNames = ["room_id", "user_id"])]
)
class CallParticipant(
    @Id @GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)
    val id: Long = 0,

    @ManyToOne(fetch = FetchType.LAZY)
    @JoinColumn(name = "room_id", nullable = false)
    val room: CallRoom,

    @ManyToOne(fetch = FetchType.LAZY)
    @JoinColumn(name = "user_id", nullable = false)
    val user: User,

    @Enumerated(EnumType.STRING)
    @Column(nullable = false, length = 10)
    val role: ParticipantRole = ParticipantRole.GUEST,

    @Column(name = "joined_at", nullable = false)
    val joinedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @Column(name = "left_at")
    var leftAt: LocalDateTime? = null,

    @Column(name = "duration_sec")
    var durationSec: Int? = null,

    @Column(name = "is_muted", nullable = false)
    var isMuted: Boolean = false
)

enum class ParticipantRole { HOST, GUEST }
```

### Redis 캐시 키 설계 - 음성 통화

```
# 활성 Room 정보 (TTL: Room 종료 시 삭제, 또는 2시간)
room:active:{roomUid}                  → Room JSON (상태, 참여자 목록 등)
room:participants:{roomUid}            → SET (userId 목록)
room:user:{userId}                     → roomUid (현재 참여 중인 방)

# 발신 중인 콜 (TTL: 30초 - ringing timeout)
call:ringing:{callId}                  → Call JSON

# 통화 통계 (TTL: 24시간)
user:call_stats:{userId}:{date}        → Hash {total, duration_sum, completed}

# 대기열 (매칭 대기 중인 사용자)
call:waiting_queue:{gender}:{purpose}  → ZSET (score: waitingSince, member: userId)
```

### DynamoDB 설계 - 음성 통화 이력

실시간 통화 세션 관리와 대용량 이력 조회에 DynamoDB 활용.

```
테이블명: maum-call-sessions

PK (Partition Key): userId           # String
SK (Sort Key):      joinedAt#roomId  # String (예: "2026-02-27T10:00:00#abc-123")

Attributes:
  roomUid       String
  roomType      String
  role          String
  durationSec   Number
  endReason     String
  callerId      String
  calleeId      String
  createdAt     String (ISO-8601)

GSI-1: roomUid-index
  PK: roomUid
  SK: joinedAt
  → 특정 방의 모든 참여자 조회

GSI-2: createdAt-index
  PK: userId
  SK: createdAt
  → 사용자별 통화 이력 최신순 조회

# 접근 패턴
- 특정 사용자의 최근 통화 이력 N건 조회    → PK=userId, SK begins_with 날짜
- 특정 방의 참여자 목록 조회               → GSI-1
- 월별 통화 집계                          → Filter + Scan (배치용)
```

---

## 3. 소셜 기능 도메인

### MySQL 스키마

**follows 테이블**
```sql
CREATE TABLE follows (
    id           BIGINT  NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    follower_id  BIGINT  NOT NULL COMMENT '팔로우를 하는 사용자',
    following_id BIGINT  NOT NULL COMMENT '팔로우를 받는 사용자',
    created_at   DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    CONSTRAINT fk_follows_follower  FOREIGN KEY (follower_id)  REFERENCES users(id),
    CONSTRAINT fk_follows_following FOREIGN KEY (following_id) REFERENCES users(id),
    UNIQUE KEY uq_follow (follower_id, following_id),
    INDEX idx_follower_id  (follower_id),
    INDEX idx_following_id (following_id),
    INDEX idx_created_at   (created_at)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
```

**likes 테이블**
```sql
CREATE TABLE likes (
    id         BIGINT  NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    liker_id   BIGINT  NOT NULL COMMENT '좋아요를 누른 사용자',
    target_id  BIGINT  NOT NULL COMMENT '좋아요를 받은 사용자',
    created_at DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    CONSTRAINT fk_likes_liker  FOREIGN KEY (liker_id)  REFERENCES users(id),
    CONSTRAINT fk_likes_target FOREIGN KEY (target_id) REFERENCES users(id),
    UNIQUE KEY uq_like (liker_id, target_id),
    INDEX idx_liker_id  (liker_id),
    INDEX idx_target_id (target_id),
    INDEX idx_created_at (created_at)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
```

**blocks 테이블**
```sql
CREATE TABLE blocks (
    id         BIGINT  NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    blocker_id BIGINT  NOT NULL COMMENT '차단하는 사용자',
    blocked_id BIGINT  NOT NULL COMMENT '차단당한 사용자',
    reason     VARCHAR(255),
    created_at DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    CONSTRAINT fk_blocks_blocker FOREIGN KEY (blocker_id) REFERENCES users(id),
    CONSTRAINT fk_blocks_blocked FOREIGN KEY (blocked_id) REFERENCES users(id),
    UNIQUE KEY uq_block (blocker_id, blocked_id),
    INDEX idx_blocker_id (blocker_id),
    INDEX idx_blocked_id (blocked_id)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
```

**reports 테이블**
```sql
CREATE TABLE reports (
    id           BIGINT  NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    reporter_id  BIGINT  NOT NULL,
    reported_id  BIGINT  NOT NULL COMMENT '신고 대상 사용자',
    room_id      BIGINT  COMMENT '통화 중 신고 시 room_id',
    reason       ENUM('SPAM','ABUSE','HARASSMENT','INAPPROPRIATE','OTHER') NOT NULL,
    description  TEXT,
    status       ENUM('PENDING','REVIEWING','RESOLVED','DISMISSED') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'PENDING',
    resolved_at  DATETIME,
    resolved_by  BIGINT  COMMENT 'admin user_id',
    created_at   DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    updated_at   DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    CONSTRAINT fk_reports_reporter FOREIGN KEY (reporter_id) REFERENCES users(id),
    CONSTRAINT fk_reports_reported FOREIGN KEY (reported_id) REFERENCES users(id),
    INDEX idx_reporter_id (reporter_id),
    INDEX idx_reported_id (reported_id),
    INDEX idx_status (status),
    INDEX idx_created_at (created_at)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
```

**Kotlin JPA Entity**
```kotlin
@Entity
@Table(
    name = "follows",
    uniqueConstraints = [UniqueConstraint(columnNames = ["follower_id", "following_id"])]
)
class Follow(
    @Id @GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)
    val id: Long = 0,

    @Column(name = "follower_id", nullable = false)
    val followerId: Long,

    @Column(name = "following_id", nullable = false)
    val followingId: Long,

    @CreationTimestamp
    @Column(name = "created_at", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    val createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now()
)

@Entity
@Table(
    name = "blocks",
    uniqueConstraints = [UniqueConstraint(columnNames = ["blocker_id", "blocked_id"])]
)
class Block(
    @Id @GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)
    val id: Long = 0,

    @Column(name = "blocker_id", nullable = false)
    val blockerId: Long,

    @Column(name = "blocked_id", nullable = false)
    val blockedId: Long,

    @Column(length = 255)
    val reason: String? = null,

    @CreationTimestamp
    @Column(name = "created_at", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    val createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now()
)

@Entity
@Table(name = "reports")
class Report(
    @Id @GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)
    val id: Long = 0,

    @Column(name = "reporter_id", nullable = false)
    val reporterId: Long,

    @Column(name = "reported_id", nullable = false)
    val reportedId: Long,

    @Column(name = "room_id")
    val roomId: Long? = null,

    @Enumerated(EnumType.STRING)
    @Column(nullable = false, length = 20)
    val reason: ReportReason,

    @Column(columnDefinition = "TEXT")
    val description: String? = null,

    @Enumerated(EnumType.STRING)
    @Column(nullable = false, length = 15)
    var status: ReportStatus = ReportStatus.PENDING,

    @Column(name = "resolved_at")
    var resolvedAt: LocalDateTime? = null,

    @Column(name = "resolved_by")
    var resolvedBy: Long? = null
)

enum class ReportReason { SPAM, ABUSE, HARASSMENT, INAPPROPRIATE, OTHER }
enum class ReportStatus { PENDING, REVIEWING, RESOLVED, DISMISSED }
```

### Redis 캐시 키 설계 - 소셜

```
# 팔로우 관계 (TTL: 1시간)
follow:followers:{userId}              → ZSET (score: followedAt, member: followerId)
follow:following:{userId}              → ZSET (score: followedAt, member: followingId)
follow:count:followers:{userId}        → Integer
follow:count:following:{userId}        → Integer
follow:check:{followerId}:{followingId} → "1" (팔로우 여부 빠른 조회)

# 차단 목록 (TTL: 30분, 보안상 중요)
block:list:{userId}                    → SET (blockedId 목록)
block:check:{blockerId}:{blockedId}    → "1" (차단 여부)

# 좋아요 (TTL: 1시간)
like:received:{userId}                 → ZSET (score: likedAt, member: likerId)
like:sent:{userId}                     → ZSET (score: likedAt, member: targetId)
like:count:{userId}                    → Integer
like:check:{likerId}:{targetId}        → "1" (좋아요 여부)

# 상호 좋아요(매칭 트리거)
like:mutual:{userId}                   → SET (상호 좋아요 상대 목록)
```

---

## 4. 매칭 도메인

### MySQL 스키마

**match_requests 테이블**
```sql
CREATE TABLE match_requests (
    id              BIGINT  NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    requester_id    BIGINT  NOT NULL,
    target_id       BIGINT  COMMENT 'NULL이면 자동 매칭',
    match_type      ENUM('DIRECT','AUTO') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'AUTO',
    status          ENUM('PENDING','ACCEPTED','REJECTED','EXPIRED','CANCELLED') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'PENDING',
    preferred_gender ENUM('MALE','FEMALE','ANY') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'ANY',
    purpose         ENUM('FRIEND','DATING','ANY') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'ANY',
    expires_at      DATETIME NOT NULL,
